  "title": "Catering Operations Manager (Urgent Hiring!) [Sembawang | 5 days | up to $4900] - LCYL",
  "description": "<h3><strong>Catering Operations Manager (Urgent Hiring!)</strong></h3><p><strong>Work Days: 5 days (including weekends)</strong></p><p><strong>Salary: $4,300 to $4,900</strong></p><p><strong>Address: 1 Senoko Ave, Singapore 758297 (Sembawang)</strong></p><p><u><strong>Job responsibilities:</strong></u></p><ul><li>Work closely with operations, sales and kitchen team to ensure the clients’ needs are met</li><li>Oversee and monitor all operations and logistics for all catering events</li><li>Manage manpower planning to suit different catering needs</li><li>Monitor service, food and beverage standards and resolve any issues if necessary</li><li>Build and maintain good working relationship with clients and handle customer complaints</li><li>Monitor and maintain vehicle standard, food quality, service standard & smooth running of the catering office and central kitchen</li><li>Understanding with and complying with the mandatory hygiene standards and requirements</li></ul><p><u><strong>Requirements:</strong></u></p><ul><li>At least 5 year(s) of working experience in catering line or hotel catering services</li><li>Possess Diploma/GCE ‘A’ or ‘O’ Level</li><li>Willing to work shifts, weekends and public holidays</li><li>Class 3 driving license </li></ul><p><br />Cheong Yeat Long | R25145358</p><p>The Supreme HR Advisory Pte Ltd | EA 14C7279</p>",
